Author: CariOS
Title: [ANN][ICO][BOUNTY]CariOS - Blockchain for Car Data Market
Body: First of all, thank you for your interest Actually, the specific detail is described in white paper. In short, I would like to summarize as below : 1) Reverse ICO for cooperation among and car IoT company, car manufacturer and capital fund in China.     It does not guarantee the success of this project, however, maybe you know how the potential market is developed. 2) This coin can be used in our real life, many instances are introduced in white paper.     The key is sustainable ecosystem of CariOS.     a - Car users provide Car data and receive the Coin as reward.     b - Car manufacturers and service providers purchase the data.     c - The data is to be processed and it creates much more values such as the pattern of car driver, road traffic, music preference, and so on.     d - Car users make the payment the Coin with the partnership of gas station.     e - All these behaviors can improve our way of life. 3) CariOS team's technology and experience can lead to success of this project. CariOS wallet is collection of car data with blockchain.  You can refer the more detail in white paper. I hope my explanation could be enough to make you more interested. Please join the telegram group

Author: CariOS
Title: [ANN][ICO][BOUNTY]CariOS - Blockchain for Car Data Market
Body: CariOS CoinBTC  Blockchain for the CAR DATA Market  ================================================== Community Link       ================================================== What is CariOS coin?   Participants in the CariOS Market are all stakeholders within the automobile industry be it car users, automobile manufacturers, or automotive service providers. They participate in CariOS Market simultaneously as data producers and consumers in a cycle of value sharing and creation. A technology-enabled economic system, CariOS Market is built on the CariOS Blockchain and supports the fair valuation of data and distribution of rewards. Accounting for adjustments in supply and demand, payouts and purchases are made with CariOS Coin.  ================================================== Why CariOS Coin?  1) Car data market with real consumers and producers - Check out our partnerships 2) The true value of CariOS Coin - Can be used in real transactions 3) A virtuous cycle of car data transactions in which all participants benefit - A sustainable ecosystem  ================================================== How CariOS ecosystem works?   VIDEO ================================================== Roadmap  ================================================== Partnership   H. Capital designed by the LD Capital is an investment institution  that provides capital investment banking services for high quality block chain projects in global market. it mainly engaged in the innovation project investment of block chain, the block chain investment bank, the incubating innovation of block chain businessÔºå actively exploring the innovation business of the block chain and so on. The headquarters is located in Singapore and selected as the OKEx super node. Investment cases: TAC traceability chain, hash world, pivot app (PVT), Content OS (cheetah), etc.   True North Venture Partners invests in and supports early stage businesses that have the potential to transform, expand and lead global industries. Our goal is to identify exceptionally talented entrepreneurs with the vision, drive and business potential to significantly improve the world and help them realize their dreams by providing capital and expertise.   Draper Dragon - Established in March of 2006, DFJ DragonFund was the joint venture between the internationally recognized venture capital firm Draper Fisher Jurvetson (DFJ) and DragonVenture, which helped pioneer venture capital in China in the late 90‚Äôs. Since its inception, DFJ DragonFund managed two US Dollar funds ‚ÄúDFJ DragonFund I & DFJ DragonFund II‚Äù and one RMB fund. In 2014, the DFJ Global Network rebranded as the Draper Venture Network. With the launch of our 3rd US Dollar fund in 2016, DFJ DragonFund henceforward became known as DraperDragon. Representative Investment Examples - Vechain, ledger, aelf, quark, etc.   HAIMA - Originally founded as a joint venture between the Hainan provincial government and Mazda, Haima Automobile was separated from the latter and became an independent brand in the Chinese market. It‚Äôs a strong player in the SUV segment.   HAWTAI - Headquartered in Beijing, China, Hawtai Motor Group manufactures finished vehicles including SUVs, sedans, station wagons, and electric vehicles (EVs), boasting an annual manufacturing capacity of 1 million vehicles. It is ranked as one of China‚Äôs top 10 automobile brands.   JMC - Once a player specializing in commercial vehicles and SUVs, Jiangling Motors (JMC) has recently begun to focus more on EVs, becoming one of the top 5 EV manufacturers in China in terms of sales rate. It currently has a joint venture with Ford.  ================================================== Sale detail  1) ICO Period : Sep. 1 - Oct. 31         2) Price : 1ETH = 60,000 CAS               Tier 1 - Bonus 30% (Sep. 1 - 14)       Tier 2 - Bonus 20% (Sep. 15 - 29)     Tier 3 - No Bonus (until Oct. 31)   3) Total Supply : 10 bil.                     4) Sales Supply : 4 bil. (40%)           5) Hard Cap : $25 mil.                                  ================================================== Team   ================================================== Bounty program  - Participants must join the official CariOS Coin Telegram group - Participants must follow and add CariOS as a friend  1) Five most active ambassadors, selected every 2 weeks = 4,000,000 CariOS Tokens for each person 2) Translation into other languages = 1,000,000 CariOS Tokens & 1,000 bounty points (Before starting the translation, please obtain the admin.'s approval) 3) Posts in Reddit, Bitcointalk and Medium = 10,000 CariOS Tokens and 10 bounty points for each (one post per person) 4) Likes and retweets on Twitter and likes on Facebook (all three) = 5,000 CariOS Tokens and 5 bounty points 5) Introduction to CariOS Coin = 5 bounty points for each recommendation; new members must name their recommenders when joining the Telegram group  Bounty tokens will be distributed within 1 week after every 2 weeks. To claim the bounty tokens, please send an e-mail with the following information with reference. officialcariosnet@gmail.com 1) Telegram ID : 2) Twitter and Facebook IDs : 3) Reddit, Bitcointalk, and Medium IDs : 4) Ethereum address : 5) Snapshots and links as evidence
